{"tid":1791274,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黑警：大埔開槍與示威活動無關","createTime":"2019-12-20T16:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T18:22:19.000Z","uid":128430,"like":36,"dislike":115,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"62f9691fbefd8d60a2450bee604bf57fd4bdbb0a","tid":1791274,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:12:40.000Z","msg":"大埔有便衣警拘一人，現場有人開槍。事件引起大量市民聚集。<br />\n<br />\n大量市民聚集初期，有警員大叫不是警方開槍，但無助令民眾散去，人群越聚越多。後來警方舉藍旗，有警員開咪稱「警方正處理一宗嚴重案件，與示威活動無關」，喝令民眾散去。其後警方更舉黑旗發射催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n現時案發現場已被防暴警員封鎖，事件起因仍然未知。<br />\n<br />\n來源：蘋果日報"},{"pid":"bdd9ac0e987b8d0ec2cd2e8cbe51881118cc1da2","tid":1791274,"uid":128430,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9k3hwFJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9k3hwFJ.jpg&h=31e4c311&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KqOM9sp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKqOM9sp.jpg&h=92ee66de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2BRKV7p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2BRKV7p.jpg&h=b5f4809d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7GfDf7q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7GfDf7q.jpg&h=0cf626f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92abe7f6eb92c2156c8cf4fdb1d29332f9de11e4","tid":1791274,"uid":53062,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:13:54.000Z","msg":"誠信破產，講咩都冇用"},{"pid":"c530a9c9219ee6eeff4976836d90d18ffa90ce33","tid":1791274,"uid":258696,"like":30,"dislike":3,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:14:08.000Z","msg":"喝令民眾？<br />\n低等毅進仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a87b809cf665839d2b4e7e4041154709365e38","tid":1791274,"uid":58841,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:14:12.000Z","msg":"講唔掂就射tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/zzz.gif